description: FINAL RELEASE -Last Terrace Home Available at 135 Seaport! This is the only developer held 3 bed, 3.5 bath residence available and features a stunning southeast exposure with panoramic views of the Blue Hills. Enjoy 427 sq ft of private outdoor terrace space equipped with a gas line for grilling. Interior finishes include wide plank ivory oak flooring, Thermador integrated appliances, and a custom Italian kitchen. Includes 2 garage parking spaces. EchelonSeaport offers over 50,000 SF of indoor and outdoor resident-only amenities, including 1 indoor and 2 outdoor pools, a state-of-the-art fitness center with indoor basketball court, yoga studio, and sports simulator. The Club Level features a fireplace lounge, library, private dining room, and expansive terraces with fire pits and grill stations. Residents enjoy 24/7 concierge, doorman, and porter services, plus onsite retail and dining. This is luxury living at its finest in Boston’s most dynamic neighborhood.
